data.description: Don't miss your opportunity to own this gorgeous home, sitting on just under 11 acres, and abounding with peace and serenity.  Entertain friends as you watch the sunset from your covered back patio.  Sit for hours on the dock and watch the horses roam and the ducks swim in your very own stocked pond. Three bedrooms 2-1/2 baths with a 15x15 office/loft area & huge 25x18 bonus room that has endless possibilities. Soaring ceilings, hardwood floors, SS appliances, stone fireplace.  No city taxes.
